one issue with RS direct interpolation is with zero diagonals (and no positive entries):  e.g.

```
            T sum_all_pos = 0, sum_all_neg = 0;
            T diag = 0;
            for(I jj = Ap[i]; jj < Ap[i+1]; jj++){
                if (Aj[jj] == i){
                    diag += Ax[jj];
                } else {
                    if (Ax[jj] < 0)
                        sum_all_neg += Ax[jj];
                    else
                        sum_all_pos += Ax[jj];
                }
